<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>κυρίᾳ μου μητρὶ Θαήσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι Ἡ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ρ</unclear>α-

    <lb n="2"/>κλε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ί</supplied>δης <choice><corr>υἱὸς</corr><sic>υιω</sic></choice> πλεῖστα χ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αίρ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ει</supplied>ν.

    <lb n="3"/>τὸ προσκύνημά σου ποιῶ καθ᾽ ἑ-

    <lb n="4"/>κάστην ἡμέραν παρὰ τῷ κυρίῳ

    <lb n="5"/>θε<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ῷ</supplied>. μὴ ἀμελήσεις οὖν <choice><corr>ἐνοχλή-

    <lb n="6"/>σειν</corr><sic>ενοχλησον</sic></choice> αὐτοῖς. ἔντελλε <choice><corr>Ἀρτεμιδώρῳ</corr><sic>αρτεμιδωρου</sic></choice>

    <lb n="7"/>ὅτι καθὼς εἰρήκαμέν σοι ὅτι μὴ

    <lb n="8"/>ἀμελήσεις· ἐὰν ἀπέ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear>χῃ ἡ πρώτη

    <lb n="9"/>ἡμέρα τῆς <choice><corr>ἑορτῆς</corr><sic>ιορτης</sic></choice> μὴ ἀφῇς αὐτοῖς

    <lb n="10"/>μηδεμίαν ἡμέραν. ἐὰν μάθῃς

    <lb n="11"/>οὖν ὅτι οὐκ <choice><corr>ἐφρόντικάν σε</corr><sic>αιφροντικαν σαι</sic></choice>, ὕ-

    <lb n="12"/>παγε πρὸς τὸν <choice><corr>λογιστὴν</corr><sic>λογιστης</sic></choice> καὶ ἔν-

    <lb n="13"/>τυχε αὐτῷ ὅτι <choice><corr>ἢ</corr><sic>ει</sic></choice> δός μοι τοὺς ἀρτο-

    <lb n="14"/>κόπους <choice><corr>ἢ</corr><sic>ει</sic></choice> δός μοι γράμματα πρὸς

    <lb n="15"/>Διονυσόδωρον· ὅτι καὶ μὴ ἀμελήσεις

    <lb n="16"/>περὶ τοῦ <choice><corr>ἐλαίου</corr><sic>αιλεου</sic></choice>. <choice><corr>ἀσπάζομαι</corr><sic>ασπαζομε</sic></choice> τὴν

    <lb n="17"/>ἀδελφήν μου. ὕπαγε πρὸς τὸν

    <lb n="18"/>ἑψατήν μου <subst><add place="inline">Μ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ώ</unclear>ρου <note lang="en" place="not specified">?</note></add><del rend="corrected">μ<del rend="erasure"><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del>ρου</del></subst> τὸν <choice><corr>χειριστὴν</corr><sic>χ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>ριστην</sic></choice>

    <lb n="19"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ὑπάγει</corr><sic>υπαγι</sic></choice> τῷ λογιστῇ καὶ <choice><corr>βάλλει</corr><sic>βαλλι</sic></choice>

    <lb n="20"/>αὐτοὺς ἔξω. ὑπηρέτησον τὰ

    <lb n="21"/><choice><corr>ὀρνίθια</corr><sic>ορνιτια</sic></choice>. μὴ πωλήσεις οὖν ἐ-

    <lb n="22"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ξ</unclear> αὐτῶν ἄχρι ἔλθω. ἐρρῶσθαί σε

    <lb n="23"/><choice><corr>εὔχομαι</corr><sic>ευχομε</sic></choice> πολλοῖς <expan>χρ<ex cert="high">όνοις</ex></expan>.
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="24"/><expan>ἀπόδ<ex cert="high">ος</ex></expan> <choice><corr>Θαήσει</corr><sic>θαησις</sic></choice> <expan>παρ<ex cert="high">ὰ</ex></expan> Ὡρίωνος <choice><corr><expan>κλιβ<ex cert="high">ανέως</ex></expan></corr><sic>κλειβ</sic></choice>.</ab></div></div><div n="meta.78595" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.78595" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="350" notBefore="301" type="textDate">1. Hälfte IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.78595" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">65</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">4493</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">78595</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">65</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">4493</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;65;4493" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.78595" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.78595" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.78595" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH01479a627da0aae83c283dc5"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>